  "statement": {
    "markdown": "Given a doubly linked list and a new node with a given value, insert the new node before the head of the list. The list is represented as a sequence of node values. The new node value is also given. The task is to output the modified list after the insertion. The head of the list is the first node in the sequence. The output should be the sequence of node values in the modified list.",
    "inputFormat": "The first line contains the number of nodes in the list. The second line contains the values of the nodes in the list. The third line contains the value of the new node to be inserted.",
    "outputFormat": "The output should be the sequence of node values in the modified list, one value per line, with the count of nodes on the line immediately before the sequence.",
    "notes": "The input list can be empty. The new node should be inserted before the head of the list, if the list is not empty. If the list is empty, the new node becomes the head of the list.",
