    "title": "Insert Before Head in DLL",
    "intuition": "The problem requires inserting a new node before the head of a doubly linked list. The brute force approach involves traversing the list to find the head, then updating the head and the new node's pointers. However, this can be optimized by simply adding the new node at the beginning of the list and updating the head.",
